{"_id":"MN3pvUSABAznj4uM","name":"Arcane Background (Sorcerer)","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n<h2>Arcane Background (Sorcerer)</h2>\n<div>\n<ul class=\"red-bullet-list\">\n<li><strong>Edge:</strong> @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Arcane Background (Sorcerer)]{Arcane Background (Sorcerer)}</li>\n<li><strong>Requirements:</strong> @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-edges.Sorcerer]{Sorcerer}</li>\n<li><strong>Arcane Skill:</strong> @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Spellcasting]{Spellcasting} (linked to @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.4 Traits]{Spirit})</li>\n<li><strong>Backlash: </strong>When a Sorcerer rolls a @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Trait Rolls]{Critical Failure} on a @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-skills.Spellcasting]{Spellcasting} roll, the Dungeon Master rolls on the @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules-tables.Sorcery Backlash]{Sorcery Backlash} to see what happens.</li>\n<li><strong>Starting Powers: 2</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Power Points: </strong>15</li>\n<li><strong>Available Powers:</strong>\n<div class=\"available-powers\">\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Analyze Foe]{Analyze Foe}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Arcane Protection]{Arcane Protection}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Augury]{Augury}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Banish]{Banish}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Barrier]{Barrier}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Beast Friend]{Beast Friend}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Blast]{Blast}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Blind]{Blind}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-powers.Bolt]{Bolt}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eber