{"_id":"YU1UTBg9bfeVwQKw","name":"Monk","content":"<p>Beginning with a foundation of mental and physical discipline, a monk channels energy to force an impossible action to become possible, from moving with superhuman speed to striking with fists of flame. The monk focuses power within them and becomes a conduit with the strictest discipline.</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Athletics, Fighting, Faith or Psionics, Notice, Religion, Stealth</p>\n<p><strong>Background Edges:</strong> Arcane Background (Miracles or Psionics), Fleet-Footed, Quick</p>\n<p><strong>Combat Edges:</strong> Counterattack, Improved Counterattack, Free Runner, Martial Artist, Martial Warrior</p>\n<p><strong>Leadership Edges:</strong> Something</p>\n<p><strong>Power Edges:</strong> Holy/Unholy Warrior</p>\n<p><strong>Professional Edges:</strong> Acrobat, Guardian, Holy Adept</p>\n<p><strong>Social Edges:</strong> Strong Willed, Iron Will</p>\n<p><strong>Weird Edges:</strong> Chi, Danger Sense</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"journal-links":{"references":{}},"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.hUQGZcxPSlD3LK6T"},"cf":{"id":"temp_pkglbsbzxv","path":"Savage Eberron Rules#/CF_SEP/1. Character Creation#/CF_SEP/1.2. Character Concepts","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"Yf8BfBpm9ugtGZrf","name":"Soak Rolls","content":"<div class=\"sweb-core\">\n  <h2>Soak Rolls</h2>\n  <p>\n    After taking damage but before applying any Wounds, the defender may spend a\n    @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Bennies]{Bennies} to make a “Soak” roll. \n    This is a @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.7 Trait Summaries]{Vigor} check, with each success and @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Raises]{raise} \n    reducing the number of @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Wounds]{Wounds} suffered from that attack by one.\n  </p> \n  <img src=\"/modules/swpf-core-rules/assets/art/redemption.webp\" class=\"float-right\" style=\"shape-outside:url(/modules/swpf-core-rules/assets/art/redemption.webp)\" />\n  <p>\n    If the character Soaks <em>all</em> of the @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Wounds]{Wounds} from an attack, he removes\n    his @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Shaken]{Shaken} condition too (even from a previous source). Don’t count the\n    Wound modifiers he’s <em>about</em> to suffer when making this roll--that\n    hasn’t happened yet.\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    Characters can’t Soak more than once per attack, but may spend  @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Bennies]{Bennies} as\n    usual to reroll the @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.7 Trait Summaries]{Vigor} check if they aren’t satisfied with the results.\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Shaken:</strong> A character can spend a Benny to immediately\n    eliminate a @Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.Shaken]{Shaken} condition. This is instant and can be done at any time.\n  </p>\n  <p>@Compendium[savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.2 Combat]{See full rules here}</p>\n</div>","img":"https://assets.forge-vtt.com/5f43f8ea1a91d63438d13159/artwork/icons/sweb-logo.webp","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DX8acFfCTTwwzgWq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_aeejh0xnzv6","path":"Savage Eberron Rules#/CF_SEP/3. Rules#/CF_SEP/Combat keywords","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.savage-eberron-rules.savage-eberron-rules.r9z2vajGx5OjXqPT"}}}
